(d) Skip ‚Äî just reviewing
```

#### Step 4: Apply to Context

**If (a) Add to 1:1 prep:**
- Update the 1:1 prep section in today's daily report
- Merge priorities with existing items
- Add asks to "Their Asks of Me" table
- Add blockers to "Blockers & Support Needed"
- Note enjoyed items for positive conversation starters

**If (b) Add to daily notes:**
- Append formatted check-in to Notes & Capture Space

**If (c) Save for next 1:1:**
- Create follow-up item: "[Name] ‚Äî Review TeamSpace check-in at next 1:1"

